Initialize lattice with PDF¶

In [ ]:
pdf = np.zeros((9, size_y, size_x))
# streaming directions/channels: east(1), south(4), south-east(8)
pdf[[1, 4, 8], :3, :3] = 1
lattice = LatticeBoltzmann(size_x, size_y, init_pdf=pdf)
